text:
Good bowl of prawn noodle in the west. The texture of the beehoon and noodles was great. Sauce and soup is on the darker side.

Plus point is that the coffee shop has mega size ceiling fan, so won't be sweating over the noodles.

A Must-Try!
Their prawn noodles are simply amazing! The broth is flavorful, the prawns are fresh, and the noodles are cooked perfectly. A must-try for prawn noodle lovers. Be prepared for a short wait, but it's worth it.
Noodles is yummy. Pork ribs & slice pork is too dry though. The guy often go for smoke breaks. Never wear mask when preparing food also. Too many houseflies at their stall.
Two very tasty bowls of prawn mee and pig's tail mee.  The beehoon mee is cooked just nice and the soup is just nice and not too salty.  Generous portion for the price range.

Travelled to Bukit Batok and ordered, only to realise itâ€™s Silat Avenue??

Average prawn mee, though generous portion when asked to add noodles.
